title: SPY SNOWX 2013
description: SPY's foray into the world of SnowX goggles came to fruition with the help of Snowcross World Champion Tucker "T-Train" Hibbert and SPY's official eyewear sponsorship of the 2012/13 ISOC Racing Series. Together, we took the best attributes of our bad to the bone MX goggles and fused them with snow technologies that we have pioneered and hung our hats on for over a decade. These ain't your mommas SnowX goggles.
